<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.4.10">
<l>vaṇṭamaruñ cōlai vayalāli naṉṉāṭaṉ</l>
<l>kaṇṭacīr veṉṟik kaliya ṉolimālai</l>
<l>koṇṭal niṟavaṇṇaṉ kaṇṇa purattāṉai</l>
<l>toṇṭarōm pāṭa niṉaintūtāy kōltumpī.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Twiggy dragonfly, sip and think of the one whose complexion is the color of clouds,</l>
<l>The one of Kaṇṇapuram, as we who are devotees</l>
<l>Sing this garland of words by victorious Kaliyaṉ with manifest fame,</l>
<l>The good one of Āli country with fields and groves where bees settle.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
